info.description:
This is a quick spare afternoon's attempt at another nz tv_grabber.
  Because the nzoom one stopped working as it was getting redirected to this source.
  Note: it is non-configurable.

  Note Also:
  The source seems to be a little unreliable.
  The guides will sometimes be completely empty.

  You may be better off using the primary NZ grabber nz_xtra.
  http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=87433&package_id=127118
info.keywords: python xmltv grabber nz New Zealand
info.name: pytvgrab-nz_tvnz
info.summary: python xmltv grabber for New Zealand (source - http://tvnz.co.nz)
